description	"Zam Wessell

Class Summary: 
A high-damage high-accuracy class with a powerful 2-shot sniper and heavy pistol.

Weaponry:
- Blaster Pistol (3)
- Thermal Detonator (1)
- Zam's Sniper Rifle (two shots per clip)
- Poison Darts (3)

Inventory:
- Binoculars
- Shape-Shifting Disguise (saber style/gun mode in melee)

Attributes:
- Heal (2)

Zam Wesell was a shapeshifting Clawdite bounty hunter from the planet Zolan. First a competitor to Jango Fett, then a professional partner in bounty hunting, Zam Wessell used her shapeshifting and sniping skills to great effect in her career thus earning Jango's trust and respect."